title: Klaus Wunderlich - 1973 - Hits Again, vol. 4 [SLE 14 723-P]
description:
Klaus Wunderlich. 
For people with musically fine-tuned ears and broad accept of music.

Volume 4 from 1973 in the Hits Again series. Comprises of medleys with covers of artists like Gilbert O'Sullivan, Cliff Richard, Demis Roussos, Albert Hammond, Tony Orlando, Mocedades and more.
